data.description: Beautiful ranch home in secluded setting. Windows stretching to top of vaulted ceiling provide marvelous light and amazing opportunities to soak in nature on the 6 + acre property. Multiple outbuildings provide a wealth of storage and room for hobbies in the 1020 sq ft shop, and chicken coop. Overlook the generous garden space from the 660 sq ft deck. Master bath w/ jetted tub and full bath off 2nd bedroom. Lovely window covered sun room, and office w/view. In Lewis County, Rochester schools.
